        "mmx_texteditor": {
            "component_code": "mmx-text-editor",
            "item_code": "mmx_texteditor",
            "settings": {
                "content": {
                    "value": "<div class=\"charge-pipe-features\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"color: #004aad; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\">Sinister Diesel Cold Air Intakes</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Features</h3>\r\n    <ul style=\"list-style: disc; margin-left: 20px;\">\r\n        <li><strong>6061 Aluminum Alloy Construction</strong> \u2013 Built for strength and longevity.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>CNC Mandrel Bent Tubing</strong> \u2013 Ensures smooth airflow and a perfect fit</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Oversized, Long-Lasting Filter</strong> \u2013 Provides excellent filtration while maximizing airflow</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Improved Throttle Response and Turbo Spool-Up</strong>Ideal for Daily Driving, Towing, or whatever your needs are</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Powder Coated in Signature Sinister Blue</strong> \u2013 A durable, polished finish for enhanced protection and style.</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Polished and Powdercoated in Sinister Blue</strong> \u2013 Adds durability and style under the hood</li>\r\n        <li><strong>Made in the USA</strong> \u2013 Ensuring top-tier craftsmanship and quality control.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Benefits</h3>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Our Cold Air Intakes are a must-have upgrade to enhance the performance of any diesel truck. Our intake systems significantly improve airflow, throttle response, and turbo spool-up, providing increases horsepower and torque.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Built with high-quality materials, our intakes are engineered for long-lasting durability. Whether you're daily driving, towing, or perparing for race day, this cold air intake delivers unmatched performance and durability.  \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Made from precision CNC Mandrel-bent aluminum tubing and paired with an oversized filter, our intake system ensures a perfect fit and maximum airflow. Polished and powder-coated in our signature Sinister Blue, it adds both corrosion resistance and an aggressive look under the hood.\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>"
                }
            }
        },
